Package edu.baylor.flarn.models

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.baylor.flarn.models.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
    @Entity
public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
    User class defines a user of the platform. A User is associated with a UserType that indicates his permissions on the system. A User can be association with other users using subscriptions.
